### ===================================================
### 🍎 Food Expiry Tracker — API Test Suite
### Dùng REST Client extension (VS Code) để chạy
### Hướng dẫn: Click "Send Request" trên từng request
### ===================================================

### ===== HEALTH CHECK =====

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/

###

### ===== AUTH MODULE =====

### 2. Register — tạo tài khoản mới
# @name register
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Quang",
  "email": "quang2@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### 3. Login — đăng nhập và lấy token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "quang2@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### Lưu token từ login response
@token = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### 4. Get Me — xem thông tin user (protected)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Register — validation error (password < 6 ký tự)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "123"
}

###

### 6. Register — email đã tồn tại (409)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Quang",
  "email": "quang2@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### 7. Login — sai password (401)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "quang2@test.com",
  "password": "wrong_password"
}

###

### 8. Get Me — không có token (401)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me

###

### 9. Get Me — token sai (403)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here

###

### ===== FOOD MODULE =====

### 10. Thêm food — an toàn (safe, >3 ngày)
# @name createSafe
POST http://localhost:3000/api/foods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Sữa tươi TH",
  "quantity": 2,
  "unit": "hộp",
  "expiryDate": "2026-08-15"
}

###

### 11. Thêm food — sắp hết hạn (warning, <=3 ngày)
# @name createWarning
POST http://localhost:3000/api/foods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Bánh mì sandwich",
  "quantity": 1,
  "unit": "ổ",
  "expiryDate": "2026-06-30"
}

###

### 12. Thêm food — đã hết hạn (expired)
# @name createExpired
POST http://localhost:3000/api/foods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Phô mai cũ",
  "quantity": 1,
  "unit": "miếng",
  "expiryDate": "2026-06-01"
}

###

### 13. Thêm food — có barcode + image
POST http://localhost:3000/api/foods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Mì Hảo Hảo",
  "barcode": "8934563118037",
  "quantity": 5,
  "unit": "gói",
  "expiryDate": "2026-12-31",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/haohao.jpg"
}

###

### 14. Thêm food — validation error (thiếu name)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/foods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quantity": 1,
  "expiryDate": "2026-12-31"
}

###

### 15. Lấy tất cả foods (sorted theo expiryDate)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 16. Filter — chỉ lấy foods an toàn
GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods?status=safe
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 17. Filter — chỉ lấy foods sắp hết hạn
GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods?status=warning
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 18. Filter — chỉ lấy foods đã hết hạn
GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods?status=expired
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 19. Stats — thống kê tổng quan
GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 20. Cập nhật food (thay ID từ response #10)
@safeFoodId = {{createSafe.response.body.data.id}}
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/foods/{{safeFoodId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quantity": 5,
  "expiryDate": "2026-09-01"
}

###

### 21. Cập nhật food — không tồn tại (404)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/foods/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quantity": 99
}

###

### 22. Xóa food đã hết hạn
@expiredFoodId = {{createExpired.response.body.data.id}}
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/foods/{{expiredFoodId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 23. Xóa food — không tồn tại (404)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/foods/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ===== CRON JOB + EMAIL =====

### 24. Trigger cron thủ công — gửi email cảnh báo
### Kiểm tra console server để thấy link preview Ethereal
GET http://localhost:3000/api/test/cron

###

### ===== ERROR HANDLING =====

### 25. Route không tồn tại (404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/nonexistent

###

### 26. Food API — không có token (401)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods
